{"tid":1514422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"愛狗之人 - 護犬大行動","createTime":"2019-08-28T17:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:33:53.000Z","uid":170199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"023a38ae52718363b9bf8e5d7de638bd85919ee6","tid":1514422,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:28:57.000Z","msg":"既然政府周街裝鏡頭 咁著重市民安全<br />\n<br />\n我地作為愛狗之人 各位附近有狗的街坊都要學習政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵鏡頭長時間錄影狗屋出入口 務求保障愛狗出入平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又可以截圖同大家分享愛犬近況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好彩狗狗無性 唔知我地成日影住佢地咋 如果唔係 佢地一定好驚 大家話係咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ee80c4a71f39152aa42f6890eebe888b1eccaa","tid":1514422,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d05b3cf6fb286ce522156878ac82e152f8ed1cbe","tid":1514422,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:29:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f87445bae5e49ab17d9bc18b162d9bd92645afa","tid":1514422,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:30:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdb01b0e932315b44f3f85b7be67c656e3f1a86","tid":1514422,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4e5aa87b3c7ce44f53180e10039f594d73271e9","tid":1514422,"uid":170199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}